1
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:08,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Once there was a man who obtained everything,
the legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.</i></font>

2
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:12,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.</i></font>

3
00:00:12,890 --> 00:00:14,630
<font face="Pristina" size="65" color="#e7cdb2"><b>All my wealth and treasure?</b></font>

4
00:00:14,630 --> 00:00:16,260
<font face="Pristina" size="65" color="#e7cdb2"><b>It can be yours if you want!</b></font>

5
00:00:16,260 --> 00:00:17,400
<font face="Pristina" size="65" color="#e7cdb2"><b>Search for it!</b></font>

6
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:19,800
<font face="Pristina" size="65" color="#e7cdb2"><b>I left everything in that one place.</b></font>

7
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:22,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>People now set sail in search of romance.</i></font>

8
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,400
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!</i></font>

9
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:53,020
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Those terrifying commanders...</font>

10
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:55,570
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">didn't stand a chance!</font>

11
00:02:55,570 --> 00:02:57,130
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Just how strong are these people?!</font>

12
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:31,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Wake up!</font>

13
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,140
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Look out below!</font>

14
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:34,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is gonna be dangerous!</font>

15
00:03:38,090 --> 00:03:40,240
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Wadatsumi is...</font>

16
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">falling on us!</font>

17
00:03:56,490 --> 00:03:58,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You should've dropped him further away,
you clumsy cook!</font>

18
00:03:58,950 --> 00:04:02,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shut it!  Or else I'll drop him on your head next time!</font>

19
00:04:08,610 --> 00:04:11,600
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're amazing, Sanji!</font>

20
00:04:15,090 --> 00:04:18,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey, Chopper!  Shrink down a bit!</font>

21
00:04:18,410 --> 00:04:21,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're making my giant robot look small!</font>

22
00:04:21,170 --> 00:04:23,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Franky, that beam was awesome!</font>

23
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:27,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Was that robot actually good for anything?</font>

24
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:32,760
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Nami-san!</font>

25
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?</font>

26
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Please wear a miniskirt!</font>

27
00:04:36,540 --> 00:04:37,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shut it!</font>

28
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:46,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Exactly what I'd expect from Luffy-kun's crew.</font>

29
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:47,290
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey...</font>

30
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:49,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The N-Noah!</font>

31
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:02,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Noah is almost on top of us!</font>

32
00:05:07,670 --> 00:05:09,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Run!</font>

33
00:05:09,170 --> 00:05:12,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The island's gonna be crushed!</font>

34
00:05:12,450 --> 00:05:16,600
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If we hang around for too long,
the Neptune Army's gonna trap us in the plaza!</font>

35
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:19,630
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hurry!  Those insane commanders are gone!</font>

36
00:05:19,850 --> 00:05:20,870
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Are you alright?</font>

37
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:25,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Is it too late?!</font>

38
00:05:28,590 --> 00:05:30,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Didn't it work... Straw Hat?!</font>

39
00:05:32,300 --> 00:05:34,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Straw Hat!</i></font>

40
00:05:42,710 --> 00:05:44,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He still...</font>

41
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:49,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">isn't giving up!</font>

42
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:55,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat Luffy-san...</font>

43
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:03,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">is doing all he can...</font>

44
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:07,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">to destroy...</font>

45
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:11,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">the Noah!</font>

46
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:15,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama!</font>

47
00:06:19,210 --> 00:06:22,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If he can destroy the Noah before it crashes...</font>

48
00:06:22,050 --> 00:06:23,860
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">then the island will be saved.</font>

49
00:06:23,860 --> 00:06:25,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">But if he can't make it...</font>

50
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:30,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Fishman Island will be destroyed!</font>

51
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:33,630
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Show us what you can do, Luffy!</font>

52
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:36,070
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-san!</font>

53
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:38,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy!</font>

54
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:40,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy!</font>

55
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,570
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-kun!</font>

56
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:56,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>You have to do it, Straw Hat!</i></font>

57
00:06:57,190 --> 00:07:00,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>That's right, Straw Hat!  We're cheering for you!</i></font>

58
00:07:00,180 --> 00:07:02,290
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Hang in there, Straw Hat!</i></font>

59
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:05,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>You're human, yet you're fighting for us!</i></font>

60
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:07,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>We're not gonna run away!</i></font>

61
00:07:07,940 --> 00:07:11,140
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Hang in there, Big Brother Straw Hat!</i></font>

62
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:17,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Fishman Island is in your hands now, Straw Hat!</i></font>

63
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:19,550
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Go, Straw Hat!</i></font>

64
00:07:19,550 --> 00:07:21,700
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>We believe in you!</i></font>

65
00:07:22,290 --> 00:07:24,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Straw Hat!</i></font>

66
00:07:24,330 --> 00:07:26,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Straw Hat!</i></font>

67
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:28,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Straw Hat!</i></font>

68
00:07:29,610 --> 00:07:42,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Straw Hat!</i></font>

69
00:07:42,890 --> 00:07:44,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Stop! Noah!</i></font>

70
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:49,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Stop!</i></font>

71
00:07:57,210 --> 00:07:58,240
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama!</font>

72
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:04,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Your wounds are opening!</font>

73
00:08:04,050 --> 00:08:04,820
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Stay away!</font>

74
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:09,490
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Watch from over there!</font>

75
00:08:09,490 --> 00:08:12,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Right now, I gotta put everything I got
into destroying this thing!</font>

76
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:20,930
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Stop right there, ship!</i></font>

77
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:34,470
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Father, I'm so sorry.</font>

78
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:39,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We must destroy the Noah.  There's no other way.</font>

79
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat!</font>

80
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:44,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's the ship of promise... </font>

81
00:08:44,190 --> 00:08:47,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">but we have no other choice. Our lives are more important.</font>

82
00:08:48,050 --> 00:08:52,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Forgive us.  It looks like
we won't be able to keep our promise -jamon...</font>

83
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Joyboy.</font>

84
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,810
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Stop!</font>

85
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:03,060
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Who's there?!</font>

86
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:10,490
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama, please stop!</font>

87
00:09:10,490 --> 00:09:13,470
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama!  I beg of you, stop!</font>

88
00:09:15,370 --> 00:09:18,320
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Get out of my way, Weak-hoshi!
If I don't destroy it, the island's gonna...</i></font>

89
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:23,200
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's alright!</font>

90
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:26,580
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Of course it's not!  Everyone's still on the island!</font>

91
00:09:26,580 --> 00:09:27,820
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>The Noah has already...</i></font>

92
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,060
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>stopped!</i></font>

93
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:44,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Sea Kings?  Why?</font>

94
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:52,150
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama yelled at me again!</font>

95
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:54,660
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey, this is no time to worry about that!</font>

96
00:09:59,620 --> 00:10:03,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I don't understand it either.</font>

97
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:06,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">But...</font>

98
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">the Noah has been stopped.</font>

99
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:14,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What is this?!</font>

100
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:18,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What's going on?  The Sea Kings stopped the ship!</font>

101
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:28,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama!  Your wounds have opened!</font>

102
00:10:28,050 --> 00:10:29,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're covered in blood!</font>

103
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:37,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">W-Well... whatever.</font>

104
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:42,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">As long as... the ship stopped.</font>

105
00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:49,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm just glad... everyone's... safe.</font>

106
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama!</font>

107
00:10:53,730 --> 00:10:55,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's alright.</font>

108
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:08,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">My, what a remarkable human.</font>

109
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:12,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What a strong human.</font>

110
00:11:12,310 --> 00:11:16,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Even if we'd been late,
the island might have still been saved...</font>

111
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:20,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">but the Noah would have been completely destroyed.</font>

112
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:31,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm so glad we made it.
Good thing Princess Shirahoshi called us here.</font>

113
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:36,130
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I couldn't do anything... I was so sad.</font>

114
00:11:36,130 --> 00:11:42,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's not true.  You were touched
by the Straw Hat child's strong emotions...</font>

115
00:11:43,050 --> 00:11:44,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">and you made a wish.</font>

116
00:11:47,930 --> 00:11:51,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">An impassioned wish...</font>

117
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:57,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">that you could help him save the island.</font>

118
00:12:12,060 --> 00:12:16,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Our power is your power.</font>

119
00:12:16,430 --> 00:12:20,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You summoned us to help him.</font>

120
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,990
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">A-Attention everyone.</font>

121
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:37,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">T-This is unbelievable.
It'd take too long to explain it all...</font>

122
00:12:37,670 --> 00:12:40,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">but it's the undeniable truth.</font>

123
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:44,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Noah has stopped!</font>

124
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:50,900
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It wasn't completely destroyed either!</font>

125
00:12:53,020 --> 00:12:56,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Fishman Island... has been saved!</font>

126
00:12:58,220 --> 00:13:00,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat did it!</font>

127
00:13:29,650 --> 00:13:31,390
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Princess Shirahoshi.</font>

128
00:13:31,930 --> 00:13:37,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We've waited a long time for you to be born.</font>

129
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Me?</font>

130
00:13:39,590 --> 00:13:44,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This ship was built so we could pull it.</font>

131
00:13:44,250 --> 00:13:49,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The tale of the ship has been passed down since the old times, so that we may do so.</font>

132
00:13:49,450 --> 00:13:53,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Is that why the Noah is so big?!</font>

133
00:13:53,170 --> 00:13:53,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yes.</font>

134
00:13:54,480 --> 00:14:01,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Once every couple hundred years,
our king is born into the body of one of the merfolk.</font>

135
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,700
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I wonder why?</font>

136
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Why indeed.</font>

137
00:14:06,430 --> 00:14:08,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's you.</font>

138
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:11,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Ever since you have been born,</font>

139
00:14:11,450 --> 00:14:14,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">you have been our Queen.</font>

140
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:21,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Honorable brother!</font>

141
00:14:21,430 --> 00:14:24,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yeah... Shirahoshi... She can't be...</font>

142
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:28,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">She must be speaking with the Sea Kings!</font>

143
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:29,760
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I can't believe it!</font>

144
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:34,870
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Several Sea Kings
suddenly appeared outside of Fishman Island.</font>

145
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:38,730
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Almost as if to stop Luffy-san from destroying the Noah.</font>

146
00:14:38,730 --> 00:14:42,810
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They came to protect it.
That's what it looks like, at least.</font>

147
00:14:42,810 --> 00:14:47,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Perhaps the Noah is somehow important to them?</font>

148
00:14:47,650 --> 00:14:49,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Neptune-sama!</font>

149
00:14:51,370 --> 00:14:53,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Sea Kings.</font>

150
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:56,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So, it's finally awakened.</font>

151
00:14:57,450 --> 00:15:01,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The power that could destroy the world itself.</font>

152
00:15:03,350 --> 00:15:08,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Look.  The bubble is being absorbed by the island.</font>

153
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:11,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Humans can't survive on the ocean floor.</font>

154
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:15,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Go to him.</font>

155
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:18,820
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama!</font>

156
00:15:18,820 --> 00:15:19,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is awful!</font>

157
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:29,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Perhaps I was imagining it?</font>

158
00:15:30,770 --> 00:15:35,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That human with the hat.  He heard our voices.</font>

159
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:37,770
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He couldn't have.</font>

160
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:43,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This happened before, a little while back.</font>

161
00:15:43,190 --> 00:15:46,000
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yes, it did.</font>

162
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:51,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Rayleigh, did you hear that voice?!</i></font>

163
00:15:51,050 --> 00:15:52,370
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>What are you talking about?</i></font>

164
00:15:52,370 --> 00:15:54,560
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>We're in the complete silence of the deep sea.</i></font>

165
00:15:55,830 --> 00:16:00,060
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Who's there?!  Who's talking so far underwater?!</i></font>

166
00:16:00,710 --> 00:16:03,810
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Hey!  Show yourself!</i></font>

167
00:16:09,090 --> 00:16:10,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I wonder why.</font>

168
00:16:10,980 --> 00:16:13,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Why indeed.</font>

169
00:16:18,630 --> 00:16:20,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">S-Sea Kings?!</font>

170
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:23,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">T-They're carrying the Noah!</font>

171
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:25,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>They're gonna eat us!</i></font>

172
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:32,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The ship is badly damaged.</font>

173
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:38,700
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Can it be fixed?  Can it still still serve its purpose?</font>

174
00:16:39,170 --> 00:16:40,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Who knows?</font>

175
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:46,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">To fix it, we'd need the skills of that clan...</font>

176
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:49,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">but times have changed.</font>

177
00:16:50,350 --> 00:16:52,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Can it be fixed?</font>

178
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hopefully it will be fixed...</font>

179
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:59,020
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">before the promised time comes.</font>

180
00:17:04,150 --> 00:17:06,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is Ryuuguu Palace!  Come in, Left Minister!</font>

181
00:17:06,050 --> 00:17:08,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We have an urgent report for you!</font>

182
00:17:08,450 --> 00:17:09,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What happened?</font>

183
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:12,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The mermaids who were kidnapped...</font>

184
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:15,730
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">have been found inside of the castle!</font>

185
00:17:15,730 --> 00:17:19,560
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?!  So, are they alright?!</font>

186
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:23,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yes.  They're a little dazed,</font>

187
00:17:23,860 --> 00:17:26,730
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">but they say they can
remember the face of their captor clearly!</font>

188
00:17:27,060 --> 00:17:30,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Unfortunately, the treasure room
was found empty at the same time.</font>

189
00:17:30,670 --> 00:17:34,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">There isn't anything left at all.</font>

190
00:17:34,530 --> 00:17:37,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Of course, this includes
the national treasure, the Tamate Box!</font>

191
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:41,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Your Majesty!</font>

192
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:45,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It appears someone has robbed us
while we were away!</font>

193
00:17:45,670 --> 00:17:48,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Never mind some petty thief stealing treasure.</font>

194
00:17:48,910 --> 00:17:53,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We could have lost the entire country
just now -jamon.</font>

195
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:59,660
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">More importantly,
tell everybody that the girls are safe.</font>

196
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:04,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It might be a little late, but we must show that the Straw Hats are innocent.</font>

197
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:07,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We've done something terrible.</font>

198
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:16,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If anyone tries to use bubbles to escape...</font>

199
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:18,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'll shoot them down!</font>

200
00:18:18,510 --> 00:18:19,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Dammit!</i></font>

201
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:23,550
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Have mercy, Boss!  Let us go!</font>

202
00:18:23,550 --> 00:18:26,100
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I was just scared of Hody and his bunch!</font>

203
00:18:26,100 --> 00:18:27,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We can go, right?!</font>

204
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:30,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We don't have anything to do with
the conflict on this island!  We're just humans!</font>

205
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:35,530
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This island depends on tourism and
the money it gets from human pirate visitors, right?!</font>

206
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:37,570
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Let us go!</font>

207
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:41,760
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I never said that we'd kill you.</font>

208
00:18:43,030 --> 00:18:46,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Wait for the Neptune Royal Family's judgment.</font>

209
00:18:48,930 --> 00:18:53,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is an announcement for all citizens.</font>

210
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:56,470
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Straw Hat Pirates...</font>

211
00:18:56,470 --> 00:19:00,110
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">had no involvement in the kidnapping of the mermaids.</font>

212
00:19:02,150 --> 00:19:07,290
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We admit that we did not check the facts properly.</font>

213
00:19:07,290 --> 00:19:11,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We truly regret it,
and would like to offer our sincerest apologies.</font>

214
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:15,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Straw Hats didn't kidnap them after all.</font>

215
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:18,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I knew they couldn't have done it all along!</font>

216
00:19:18,830 --> 00:19:20,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Don't lie!</font>

217
00:19:20,180 --> 00:19:23,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We all thought that they were the culprits.</font>

218
00:19:25,860 --> 00:19:28,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">N-No, we believed in them, right?</font>

219
00:19:28,080 --> 00:19:28,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">S-Sure.</font>

220
00:19:28,590 --> 00:19:30,120
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Liars!</font>

221
00:19:30,120 --> 00:19:31,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Quiet!</font>

222
00:19:31,180 --> 00:19:32,490
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're being unfair!</font>

223
00:19:32,490 --> 00:19:34,020
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yeah!</font>

224
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:36,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We must admit it.</font>

225
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:39,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We doubted them...</font>

226
00:19:40,100 --> 00:19:43,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We doubted them because they were human!</font>

227
00:19:44,250 --> 00:19:47,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's how it's always been.</font>

228
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We've always seen the humans as...</font>

229
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:52,990
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Super...</font>

230
00:19:52,990 --> 00:19:54,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Afro!</font>

231
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:57,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Franky-san, that is quite stylish!</font>

232
00:19:57,220 --> 00:19:58,240
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Super, isn't it?</font>

233
00:19:58,240 --> 00:20:02,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I get completely worn out
whenever I use the Monster Point,</font>

234
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:05,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">and I can't even walk for two or three hours.</font>

235
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:09,600
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">But... I can still treat your wounds.</font>

236
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:11,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Is everyone alright?</font>

237
00:20:11,350 --> 00:20:13,460
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>You</i> aren't alright.</font>

238
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:14,920
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Everyone seems fine.</font>

239
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,630
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Robin-chan!</i></font>

240
00:20:16,630 --> 00:20:19,470
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I used my ultimate technique too, so I'm completely worn out!</font>

241
00:20:19,470 --> 00:20:21,470
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Let me rest on your lap!</font>

242
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:22,930
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Pwease!</font>

243
00:20:22,930 --> 00:20:24,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Just sleep on the ground.</font>

244
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:26,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">No, you!</font>

245
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:28,140
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy.</font>

246
00:20:28,650 --> 00:20:30,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's the Princes!</font>

247
00:20:37,130 --> 00:20:38,150
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hody?!</font>

248
00:20:38,150 --> 00:20:40,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Vander Decken?!</font>

249
00:20:40,450 --> 00:20:44,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Father, you must have been worried.</font>

250
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:46,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm just glad you're safe -jamon.</font>

251
00:20:51,550 --> 00:20:55,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Everyone!  You can rest easy!</font>

252
00:20:55,340 --> 00:20:58,550
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">These men will no longer be allowed to run wild!</font>

253
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:04,700
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Now we can live without worrying!</font>

254
00:21:06,330 --> 00:21:10,860
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I can't believe someone so scary
was in the Fishman District, so close to us.</font>

255
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:14,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">C-Captain Hody!</font>

256
00:21:14,610 --> 00:21:16,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He looks like a monster!</font>

257
00:21:19,090 --> 00:21:21,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's great!</font>

258
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:26,520
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey, isn't that...</font>

259
00:21:26,520 --> 00:21:28,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He's back!</font>

260
00:21:28,590 --> 00:21:29,870
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-san!</font>

261
00:21:29,870 --> 00:21:32,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's Straw Hat Luffy and Princess Shirahoshi!</font>

262
00:21:32,890 --> 00:21:35,370
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Please, help him!</font>

263
00:21:35,370 --> 00:21:39,990
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama won't stop bleeding!</font>

264
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:45,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama pushed himself too far for our sake.</font>

265
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:46,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat.</font>

266
00:21:48,210 --> 00:21:52,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is awful!  I've got something to stop the bleeding in my backpack.</font>

267
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:54,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm counting on you, Robin.</font>

268
00:21:54,380 --> 00:21:55,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Sure.</font>

269
00:21:55,650 --> 00:21:59,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm really worried about our next fight, Doc!</font>

270
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:00,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Right, I'm ready!</font>

271
00:22:01,810 --> 00:22:02,860
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'll move you.</font>

272
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:05,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's a really freaky doctor!</font>

273
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">A little to the left... the left...</font>

274
00:22:06,950 --> 00:22:09,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Can you save Luffy-sama?!</font>

275
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:13,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I can stop the bleeding,
but he's already lost so much blood.</font>

276
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He doesn't have enough left!</font>

277
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:16,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?!</font>

278
00:22:16,050 --> 00:22:19,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy's the only one in the crew with blood type F.</font>

279
00:22:19,650 --> 00:22:20,930
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's terrible!</font>

280
00:22:20,930 --> 00:22:23,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">There must be someone else with that blood type
here in the plaza!</font>

281
00:22:23,510 --> 00:22:24,280
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Anyone!</font>

282
00:22:24,280 --> 00:22:25,690
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey!</font>

283
00:22:25,690 --> 00:22:27,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I... I've got F.</font>

284
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:29,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I have type F, but...</font>

285
00:22:29,590 --> 00:22:32,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Daddy, you're type F, right?</font>

286
00:22:32,510 --> 00:22:33,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Uh, well...</font>

287
00:22:33,890 --> 00:22:39,390
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh, right!  This country has a law against donating blood to humans!</font>

288
00:22:40,450 --> 00:22:43,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What kind of law is that?!  That's awful!</font>

289
00:22:43,650 --> 00:22:46,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Please!  Luffy's in trouble!</font>

290
00:22:48,060 --> 00:22:52,940
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">My blood type is different, but it's still red!</font>

291
00:22:52,940 --> 00:22:54,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Will that do?!</font>

292
00:22:54,210 --> 00:22:56,730
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Uh, no.  I appreciate the sentiment, at least.</font>

293
00:22:56,730 --> 00:22:58,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Princess Shirahoshi!</font>

294
00:22:58,800 --> 00:23:02,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I know!  There are some human pirates here too!</font>

295
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:14,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Use my blood.</font>

296
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:19,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's type F.  I'll give you as much as you need.</font>

297
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,580
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Jinbe!</font>

298
00:23:20,580 --> 00:23:21,560
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Jinbe-chan!</font>

299
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:23,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">But, the law...</font>

300
00:23:23,850 --> 00:23:27,060
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm a pirate.</font>

301
00:23:27,060 --> 00:23:30,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Boss!  What a relief!</font>

302
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:31,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Jinbe-san!</i></font>

303
00:23:31,180 --> 00:23:32,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Thank you!</font>

304
00:23:34,310 --> 00:23:36,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Jinbe, you-</font>

305
00:23:36,310 --> 00:23:38,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's fine -jamon.</font>

306
00:23:38,090 --> 00:23:39,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Y-Your Majesty?</font>

307
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:45,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What's the problem?  Outdated laws...</font>

308
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:47,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">are just curses.</font>

309
00:24:07,490 --> 00:24:10,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Jinbe, this'll hurt a little.</font>

310
00:24:10,040 --> 00:24:11,200
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I don't mind.</font>

311
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,730
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Even when you're hurt,</i></font>

312
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,470
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>even when you're doing the hurting,</i></font>

313
00:24:51,370 --> 00:24:54,460
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>red blood flows through your veins.</i></font>

314
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:08,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>This thin, tiny tube,</i></font>

315
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:14,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>too small to be considered a path,</i></font>

316
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:23,460
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>is what breaks through the prejudiced fear...</i></font>

317
00:25:35,150 --> 00:25:37,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>and the battles that tried to
wash away blood with more blood.</i></font>

318
00:25:43,740 --> 00:25:46,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>So easily it flows.</i></font>

319
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:52,010
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>It is not some fleeting vision in the clouds,</i></font>

320
00:25:53,030 --> 00:25:57,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>but a clearly visible path that leads to the sun.</i></font>

321
00:26:08,580 --> 00:26:10,110
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Jinbe.</font>

322
00:26:10,910 --> 00:26:13,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama, you're awake!</font>

323
00:26:13,830 --> 00:26:14,990
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Luffy!</i></font>

324
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:16,700
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Luffy!</i></font>

325
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:20,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What, you were conscious?</font>

326
00:26:24,130 --> 00:26:25,660
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Straw Hat!</i></font>

327
00:26:25,660 --> 00:26:26,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Luffy!</i></font>

328
00:26:54,650 --> 00:26:58,290
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is... our new beginning,</font>

329
00:27:02,010 --> 00:27:03,100
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Mother!</font>

330
00:27:17,630 --> 00:27:19,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey, Jinbe.</font>

331
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:34,820
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Join my crew!</font>

332
00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:39,230
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Royal Family has made its decision!</font>

333
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:43,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Alright!  We're free!</font>

334
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,770
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Serves you right, Hody!</font>

335
00:27:47,850 --> 00:27:50,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I thought I'd live the rest of my days as a slave!</font>

336
00:27:50,740 --> 00:27:54,560
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat Pirates, we owe you one!</font>

337
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:56,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm gonna become the Pirate King!</font>

338
00:27:56,890 --> 00:27:59,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Huh?!  I don't know about that...</font>

339
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:00,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Idiot!  I'm gonna do it!</font>

340
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:04,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We can finally go to the New World!</font>

341
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:08,580
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What if their grudge against Hody
turns into a grudge against Fishman Island?</font>

342
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:15,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That shouldn't change my decision.  This island
is a rest stop and tourism destination for pirates.</font>

343
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:18,560
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They didn't come here with ill intentions.</font>

344
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:21,620
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">There is no reason for us to keep them -jamon.</font>

345
00:28:21,620 --> 00:28:26,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Now then, as for the remaining members of
the New Fishman Pirates!</font>

346
00:28:26,050 --> 00:28:28,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">P-Please don't execute us!</font>

347
00:28:28,330 --> 00:28:29,810
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">S-Spare our lives!</font>

348
00:28:29,810 --> 00:28:35,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We didn't know anything about Hody murdering the Queen!</font>

349
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:37,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They're all insane!</font>

350
00:28:37,180 --> 00:28:38,990
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I sentence you...</font>

351
00:28:40,010 --> 00:28:43,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">to live here, on Fishman Island's mainland!</font>

352
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:45,010
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Whaaaaat?!</i></font>

353
00:28:45,010 --> 00:28:48,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?!  You mean to live under the law?!</font>

354
00:28:48,350 --> 00:28:51,120
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's fine by me.
It's better than being ruled by Hody.</font>

355
00:28:51,120 --> 00:28:55,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You can't do that, Your Majesty!
We can't let these guys roam the streets freely.</font>

356
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:58,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We'll be scared to let our children out of the house!</font>

357
00:28:59,860 --> 00:29:02,930
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Of course, they'll work under my army's command...</font>

358
00:29:02,930 --> 00:29:05,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">and will be pressed into service -jamon</font>

359
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:10,890
