379
00:30:20,020 --> 00:30:22,280
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Why won't you join us, Jinbe?!</font>

380
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:24,100
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Let's go on adventures together!  Please!</font>

381
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:27,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Let's go out to sea!  It'll be fun!</font>

382
00:30:27,410 --> 00:30:29,600
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yeah, join our crew, Boss!</font>

383
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:32,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">A former Warlord in our crew would be really reassuring!</font>

384
00:30:32,950 --> 00:30:35,500
