385
00:30:37,210 --> 00:30:40,490
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm only saying that I can't join you <i>yet</i>.</font>

386
00:30:41,580 --> 00:30:45,440
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm glad that you invited me.</font>

387
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:49,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm sure it would be fun
