390
00:31:02,010 --> 00:31:08,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I must still complete that journey.
Once I am able to move freely again...</font>

391
00:31:08,090 --> 00:31:13,230
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I will come to meet up with you.  This I promise you.</font>

392
00:31:14,210 --> 00:31:19,370
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If you still feel the same way when that time comes,</font>

393
00:31:19,370 --> 00:31:24,010
