398
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:51,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Thank you.</font>

399
00:31:52,340 --> 00:31:53,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So, what now?</font>

400
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:56,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Do we just head straight for the New World?</font>

401
