456
00:35:34,060 --> 00:35:36,940
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">And the Swing Jazz Orchestra!</font>

457
00:35:48,010 --> 00:35:50,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What an amazing singing voice! </font>

458
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:52,600
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Maria-sama! </font>

459
00:35:52,600 --> 00:35:55,620
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">My soul is trembling!  Oh yeah!</font>

460
00:36:05,090 --> 00:36:07,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">And our special guests!</font>

461
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:10,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">N-No way!</font>

462
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:20,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Men are left breathless by their beauty!</font>

463
00:36:33,240 --> 00:36:37,100
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Mermaid Caf√© Dancers!</font>

464
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:47,700
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Stop that!</font>

465
00:36:57,200 --> 00:36:58,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You'll die, Sanji!</font>

466
00:37:00,990 --> 00:37:04,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Beauty too pure to be captured by a mere picture!
These ladies are number one!</font>

467
00:37:06,820 --> 00:37:08,710
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">My powuh ith fadibg...</font>

468
00:37:08,710 --> 00:37:09,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh, my.</font>

469
00:37:09,510 --> 00:37:10,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Awesome!</font>

470
00:37:10,680 --> 00:37:11,770
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Simply spellbinding!</font>

471
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:15,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Caimie!</font>

472
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:18,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Ishilly!  You're alright!</font>

473
00:37:22,730 --> 00:37:25,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Finally!  Can't have a feast without this!</font>

474
00:37:27,350 --> 00:37:29,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I've been super-waiting for this!</font>

475
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:31,110
