476
00:37:32,170 --> 00:37:33,000
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Thank you very much.</font>

477
00:37:33,770 --> 00:37:34,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Most obliged.</font>

478
00:37:35,150 --> 00:37:35,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Thank you.</i></font>

479
00:37:36,240 --> 00:37:38,900
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Mermaid-chaaaan!</i></font>

480
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:43,940
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Thank you very much.</font>

481
00:37:44,080 --> 00:37:48,010
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Cheers!</i></font>

482
00:37:48,010 --> 00:37:50,520
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Now, let's start drinking!</font>

483
00:37:53,650 --> 00:37:54,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yummy!</font>

484
00:37:54,890 --> 00:37:56,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You can have as much as you like.</font>

485
00:37:56,350 --> 00:37:58,280
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh, I'm done for!</font>

486
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Sanji!</font>

487
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:05,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You should be more careful, sir.</font>

488
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Father!</font>

489
00:38:07,640 --> 00:38:08,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shirahoshi.</font>

