00:38:09,310 --> 00:38:10,550
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Cheers!</font>

491
00:38:10,990 --> 00:38:14,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Cheers -jamon!  It's alright -jamon!</font>

492
