499
00:38:37,680 --> 00:38:40,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Akkamanbo!  Fuuri!  Fuuri!</font>

500
00:38:40,670 --> 00:38:43,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Keep dancing, everyone!</font>

501
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:46,930
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Eat, drink, and let loose -mi fa so la ti do!</font>

502
00:39:03,470 --> 00:39:05,150
