505
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:16,000
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I-I should make this clear, I have sworn to love nobody but my wife, Otohime, for the rest of my life!</font>

506
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:18,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">She might be dead now, but I could never betray-</font>

507
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,660
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Who is Joyboy?</font>

508
00:39:25,540 --> 00:39:29,140
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I read a Poneglyph in the Sea Forest.</font>

509
00:39:29,290 --> 00:39:32,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Who was he apologizing to?</font>

510
00:39:34,610 --> 00:39:37,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You can read them?!</font>

511
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:42,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm a survivor from Ohara.
