00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:56,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm okay with you knowing.</font>

515
00:39:57,770 --> 00:40:04,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Joyboy was a man from the surface, who lived during the void century.</font>

516
00:40:04,180 --> 00:40:07,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So he died at least eight hundred years ago?</font>

517
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:13,610
