519
00:40:19,070 --> 00:40:21,010
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Promise?</font>

520
00:40:21,010 --> 00:40:24,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The details haven't been passed down,</font>

521
00:40:24,180 --> 00:40:30,840
