<font face="Impress BT" size="55">by the Sea Kings.</font>

529
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:07,440
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Maybe Joyboy, who was going to use the Noah, had the power to control the Sea Kings?</font>

530
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:13,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">No, it was the former Mermaid Princess
who had that power.</font>

531
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:18,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I knew it.
So, does Princess Shirahoshi have the same power?</font>

532
00:41:18,730 --> 00:41:24,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yes.  I assume that it awakened completely today.</font>

533
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:37,560
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I can't say I'm happy about this.</font>

534
00:41:37,560 --> 00:41:39,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I understand.</font>

535
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:46,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Two years ago, I read a Poneglyph on Sky Island
that told the location of an ancient weapon.</font>

536
00:41:49,030 --> 00:41:52,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It said that it was here, on this island.</font>

537
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:57,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Mermaid Princess
who lived in the same era as Joyboy...</font>

538
00:41:59,410 --> 00:42:02,320
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Is this what they called her, perhaps?</font>

539
00:42:04,620 --> 00:42:08,260
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Or in other words, Princess Shirahoshi, who carries the same power...</font>

540
00:42:08,260 --> 00:42:11,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">will also inherit this title.</font>

541
00:42:13,790 --> 00:42:16,490
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Her other name is...</font>

542
00:42:20,260 --> 00:42:21,620
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">the ancient weapon...</font>

543
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:24,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Poseidon!</font>

